00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:58,640
1.6% chance of clearing the hurdle.

223
00:15:57,440 --> 00:16:00,560
>> That is ruthless.

224
00:15:58,640 --> 00:16:06,280
>> It's brutally effective. It exposes inconsistent skills long before they touch production data.

